AFN BULLBAR – TOYOTA HILUX Revo 2020

AFN bullbar to suit Toyota Hilux AFN BULLBAR – TOYOTA HILUX Revo 2020

The pictured bullbar features;

  • Steel Construction
  • Full Bumper Replacement – Sleek form fitting design
  • Winch Compatible up to 12,000lbs
  • 2 x Rated Recovery Points
  • 2 x Hi-Lift Jack Points
  • 2 x Antenna Tabs
  • Under Bar Plates
  • 6mm Aluminium Centre Under Bar Plate
  • Fog/Indicator Light Assemblies

 

PLEASE NOTE: The above bar is suited to the wide body Toyota Hilux. Depending on stock & availability, the current wait time for this product is approx. 30 – 90 days from date of order.
